Description: =================
        django-sendcloud2
        =================
        
        提供django下sendcloud接口,支持python2/3，支持replyto
        
        Quick start
        -----------
        1. Install::
        
            pip install django_sendcloud2
        
        
        2. 配置，在settings.py中::
        
            EMAIL_BACKEND = 'sendcloud.SendCloudBackend'
            SENDCLOUD = {
                'email': {
                    'api_user': '',
                    'api_key': '',
                },
                'sms': {
                    'sms_user': '',
                    'sms_key': '',
                    'muted': True
                },
            }
        
        
        
        3. 按照正常django方式发送邮件即可， 发送sms用`sms.send`
        
